Author: omgitscynthia
Text: If this ever happens again, the blackened tenders are only 170 calories for 3 of them. And I get a side of green beans for another 55 cals. I don't care for their biscuits, so no temptation there. And ours have a Coke Freestyle machine so I get Mellow Yellow Zero with cherry syrup.

Author: cupcakelimao
Text: Hey it's one day. Your maintanance is probably way above 1200 cals, so if one day you eat a little below maintanance or just a little above, you won't gain!  It may even boost your metabolism and you'll have energy to burn even more.
